title: 820-00165 a1466
message:
Hey Guys. 

A previous repair liquid damage was working for some time and randomly would power on or not... 820-00165 A1466 no green light no power...

PP3V42_G3H - 3.4
PPDCIN_G3H - 15v
PP3V3_S5 - 0.29v

title: 820-00165 a1466
message:
What about PPBUS_G3H voltage?
Also check SMC_RSMRST_L and SMC_PM_G2_EN.

title: 820-00165 a1466
message:
Hi :)

PPBUS_G3H 8.2v
SMC_RESET_L 3.3v
SMC_PM_G2_EN no voltage

title: 820-00165 a1466
message:
Looks like SMC issue.
Reball it as first stept.
If no result, change SMC.
However test 3V42 presence around SMC.

title: 820-00165 a1466
message: 3v42 is present around SMC. There was some liquid damage in the area i renewed everything last time but maybe something under the SMC

title: 820-00165 a1466
message: 8.2 is too low should be 8.6. Reflow SMC. If no change, replace from an identical 820-00165 donor board.
